            <div class="description">
                <p>A vitamin is one of a group of organic substances that is present in minute amounts in natural
                    foodstuffs. Vitamins are essential to normal metabolism. If we do not take enough of any kind of
                    vitamin, certain medical conditions can result.
                </p>
                <p>A vitamin is both:</p>
                <p>an organic compound, which means it contains carbon</p>
                <p>an essential nutrient that body cannot produce enough of and which it needs to get from food</p>
